l_answer\\\"}\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n          \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n          \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 1150,\n            \"output\": 536,\n            \"totalTokens\": 35094,\n            \"cacheRead\": 33408,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0.019267\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774616658658,\n          \"responseId\": \"resp_091789ebac5481e50169c6805573b481919ef80a99474b1e22\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"8e719779\",\n            \"seq\": 23\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:03b29602-b584-4ec0-9241-b0d74393cc82\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: daily-atlas-os-review\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Cron: daily-atlas-os-review\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774616400010,\n      \"sessionId\": \"4d04c080-daf9-41c8-8164-3b873efd5dec\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 272000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 33420,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 1.320784,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\main\\\\sessions\\\\4d04c080-daf9-41c8-8164-3b873efd5dec.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Para WhatsApp a: +573183718246\\n\\nRevisé completo el Tasks Tracker de Notion y moví esto:\\n\\n- **Mejorar proactividad de OpenClaw (Atlas)**: estaba en **Backlog** y lo pasé a **In progress**.\\n  - Decisión/primer paso ya ejecutado: revisé `HEARTBEAT.md`.\\n  - Hallazgo real: sigue como template vacío, sin checklis