{"type":"message","id":"8172dcfe","parentId":"5098edcb","timestamp":"2026-03-28T00:03:05.627Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Clarifying communication method**\n\nI need to finalize a plain text summary, and I should note that it will go to WhatsApp instead of sending it elsewhere. I also realized that I didn't coordinate with other agents, primarily because there's no backlog or clear next steps with an owner aside from Atlas. It seems like I might need to keep track of this to ensure everything is organized properly.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_003269f6235209990169c71ab470e8819199b450dc10717c27\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpxxq3sM-hyfJbqf-1Nb3DBO45H3A7QYatzar2J5uLQNQGnR_d2rcC3N8rOgEQXMBk8SdSkNkvIXuSZdZy1VtpAKAErcG-awfRlPmPDoj8xUhg1U_7_gakmFFqcW7_yrLakrCIGvYsbg7RJThcuytNVr-HWLf7ToA0ajkrdu2I6bhSBkH1PBKky-h2M1WzID4TUZsOgsmT-eQwUFIHBFio5wAJ01BrHHZvyp6szik1kOjH3jpxKTNE8aL-t7PvjM5VPdFEeQ98hrQEfGdDLpXZBqtyzR6JRhZDrOxGSoGBNTNFjUw-17HYqeDG_o7PchcdCr0_VvTuEpxeZOM6n7MfjNGtk2hTn67ESlZa5K-u4VK_rNQSnQQJEdxDKL0HFNiQy0fht0Tb5BjffrM_NS1b59JFP1jrrShWe6yNobJcE-ZVeZhmHKGyemnOzLJODiygvSqkkpK0DsMnjmGRv62elA4gUaHtsupGCGnBBcMr4V3vCMciMTTClk1UEw6bXZoC7TgffLzvUTmDUQMKmEZR2-y1fiYOpNa7bkg2OjSwqP3nUBl7G7z2iWmSRnjaBlYcdUM7s1NqXRvX6E9z2yc5nLoLJjjHB_YS6GELhdsKsYu_L4TuuICENprAOedSikanfJJLrp0mlchsmRGMlczYVkLF9XiNpvj855IB91L46KwaWq2AnG7IoHY9KIZ-t-6KsjI73VZOvNMfj2fFWYJxXeo_ELPQ0EgsTuToIk4-NvYLN25ptl7Zcyy1fffety9Ky0aXgpSgEr-_yfPzbwsvHShTsGv1AnjHeBsF2MLdtfKVd2qkfRfcv2gv6CmvYoViBkKjb-OucvBcaM8RU9q7SMpC0fl7kRqnABoqgGO42_oLgcM0TyzI2YNWFvB9sMRZRmR2withJ7JCrACE2L09muETKruW8v2j1DvWwyGCzMrDsRnGuLSp5Z8Zx6_StaAedfr9hdkcA2TeVoYI4aKIHizSa4aoDoObmxxKZRa8gkIW5lOM3I2SgbmZ91oVJD4qGE4PeJIfbcw-ZMiVR7BrZjmpsBORsv0vqnEZeEPDgf4-0n7CpOVL8Bs0QCHhgvdHqbkV\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Clarifying communication method**\\n\\nI need to finalize a plain text summary, and I should note that it will go to WhatsApp instead of sending it elsewhere. I also realized that I didn't coordinate with other agents, primarily because there's no backlog or clear next steps with an owner aside from Atlas. It seems like I might need to keep track of this to ensure everything is organized properly.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"Para WhatsApp a +573183718246\n\nRevisé completo el Tasks Tracker y moví lo que sí tenía owner claro en Backlog/Next.\n\nQué moví:\n- Mejorar proactividad de OpenClaw (Atlas) → sigue In progress\n  - Primer paso real ejecutado: reemplacé el HEARTBEAT.md vacío por una checklist operativa corta.\n- Investigar correo con dominio gestionado en Cloudflare (Atlas) → Backlog → Waiting\n  - Dejé investigación inicial en `research/cloudflare-email-options-2026-03-27.md`.\n  - Decisión pendiente: solo reenvío gratis con Cloudflare vs inbox completa con proveedor externo.\n- Diseñar plan para volver agentes más autónomos, interactivos y productivos (Atlas) → Backlog → In progress\n  - Dejé plan concreto en `ops/agent-autonomy-plan.md`.\n- Preparar sistema para factura mensual al proveedor (Atlas) → Next → In progress\n  - Dejé esqueleto operativo en `ops/invoice-system-plan.md` con reglas, fórmula base y pendientes.\n- Automatizar recordatorio mensual para factura unos días antes de fin de mes (Atlas) → Backlog → Waiting\n  - Ya quedó definido el primer paso, pero depende de plantilla real + definir timing final.\n\nQué coordiné:\n- Hoy, en Backlog/Next con owner claro, el movimiento real era casi todo de Atlas; no encontré nuevas tareas en Backlog/Next de Prometeo, Ares o Hestia que tocaran esta ronda.\n- Igual mantuve el dashboard honesto: Ares/Hestia siguen como estaban en Blocked/Waiting/Done según evidencia previa, sin inflar avance.\n\nQué quedó bloqueado o esperando:\n- ZooLATECH sigue Blocked por falta de acceso efectivo al adjunto/correo desde este flujo.\n- Factura mensual: ya hay base, pero falta la plantilla de Gustavo.\n- Cloudflare mail: falta decidir si quiere forwarding barato o inbox completa.\n\nQué sigue:\n1. Si Gustavo define “solo reenvío” vs “inbox completa”, cierro la recomendación final de correo.\n2. Cuando llegue la plantilla de factura, paso de sistema base a borrador real.\n3. Probar 3–5 días el nuevo HEARTBEAT + plan de autonomía para ver si baja la ambigüedad y sube la ejecución real.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_003269f6235209990169c71ab757e0819190b50027d65d2713\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":136,"output":542,"cacheRead":56320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56998,"cost":{"input":0.00034,"output":0.00813,"cacheRead":0.014079999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02255}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774656171956,"responseId":"resp_003269f6235209990169c71ab155c48191aebace0857b00304"}}
